{"tid":1488191,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請推- 廣東話將被滅！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-19T14:26:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T04:56:44.000Z","uid":1206,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b958424ba560a5429b51584216e3ce287da3b545","tid":1488191,"uid":1206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:26:39.000Z","msg":"當大家仲向到嘈緊逃犯條例時，林鄭已經修改緊中文科課程，唔洗聽同講廣東話了。<br />\n<br />\n16/9諮詢期就過啦，之後拿拿聲上立法會一讀二讀三讀搞點。DQ埋d阻頭阻勢既議員。香港人你慢慢嘈逃犯條例啦，日日食催淚彈啦。<br />\n<br />\n#滅一個文化先滅佢既語言<br />\n#咁既政府管理香港，如果無左示威者，後果會係點？<br />\n#示威者既爆力係唔岩，但哩個政府真係無得救。<br />\n#你可以唔支持黃絲，但有一日香港失去核心價值時，唔好問點解。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/curriculum-development/kla/chi-edu/whats-new.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcurriculum-development%2Fkla%2Fchi-edu%2Fwhats-new.html&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAPilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=1553fc69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/curriculum-development/kla/chi-edu/whats-new.html</a><br />\n<br />\n16/9終止諮詢的是：<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/TF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Fattachment%2Ftc%2Fabout-edb%2Fpress%2Fconsultation%2FTF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAPilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=991f9f2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/TF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n🐸🐸🐸🐸🐸🐸<br />\n專責小組歡 迎 公 眾 人 士 就 本 諮 詢 文 件 所 述 的初步建議及／或與學校課程未來發展有關事宜，提出看法、意見和建議。專責小組會在制訂方向性建議時，詳細考慮所有意見和建議，並於二零一九年年底前向政府提交最後報告。<br />\n<br />\n請於二零一九年九月十六日（星期一）或之前，以郵寄、<br />\n電郵或傳真方式把書面意見交予專責小組秘書處：<br />\n郵寄地址： 香港灣仔皇后大道東 213 號胡忠大廈 13 樓 1301 室<br />\n學校課程檢討專責小組秘書處<br />\n電郵： taskforce_cur@edb.gov.hk<br />\n傳真號碼： (852) 2573 5299"},{"pid":"c5518a6e7e6f491f17c0b79c520f8b6e55af64a5","tid":1488191,"uid":1206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:27:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e034cbf7ae923709561cb13ed325f56df5ce5be3","tid":1488191,"uid":1206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:27:19.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"c1369a03e6addc14b3946dc696e85d0ac8c30f05","tid":1488191,"uid":1206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:27:31.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"e7b700aa17020e06708b0a65499a617f3e39f711","tid":1488191,"uid":206827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:27:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">阻阻大家 入黎擺低死線唔該<br />\n既然無死線做唔到野就擺低死線既日期出黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家個個話要死線 死線呢？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488086</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a2e418b3a62ab3596fb436c4246272ba7c8867ff","tid":1488191,"uid":1206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:27:50.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"c71398922bc922db3322bd387bb8062bd8372407","tid":1488191,"uid":1206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:28:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3b1847375181081146c09751dabca48f232ed9d","tid":1488191,"uid":1206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:28:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"144034f82cb472a09308fcbda9f6f75e9a760e21","tid":1488191,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:30:42.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1f1185569ca2799f7911c81322ff611c33b7ad24","tid":1488191,"uid":1206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:31:44.000Z","msg":"⼀⼁⼀⼃⼁⼂"},{"pid":"fddb35be6a589a4749a757ff1c47e9ea45f76fed","tid":1488191,"uid":1206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:31:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8e7702f1dbc82d84586fe2f3d30a7f545be0fe3","tid":1488191,"uid":1206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:32:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f41d727f1b5591bde0e6f8e0abc789afcc7c1c","tid":1488191,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:33:21.000Z","msg":"究竟佢邊段講要普教中<br />\n麻煩真係要quote出黎<br />\n非五毛<br />\n但唔想做盲目既示威者"},{"pid":"ce3a5a423d419fbdfc9ad29f7ab2f5ac7607d090","tid":1488191,"uid":1206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:38:52.000Z","msg":"【請廣傳】<br />\n<br />\n#政府趁火打劫 政府修改中文科課程，打算Cut走聆聽及說話兩卷，無疑令學生對粵語嘅敏感度同使用度減低，長遠就可以輕易消滅廣東話。當新移民學生都唔洗再努力學講廣東話，就意味住廣東話會被邊緣化，到時香港學生反被跨境學童歧視，就不再限於上水。<br />\n<br />\n即係話，新移民連譚仔話都唔洗識，直接喺你面前傻逼二貨坑爹麼麼噠，你話嘔唔嘔心？<br />\n<br />\n朋友傳來，呼籲大家積極表達意見（佢聽唔聽一件事，但嘢要做足）：<br />\n<br />\n公眾人士如對諮詢文件的初步建議有任何看法、意見及建議，需於2019年9月16日或之前，以郵寄、電郵或傳真方式把書面意見交予專責小組秘書處。<br />\n<br />\n電郵：taskforce_cur@edb.gov.hk<br />\n傳真：852- 25735299<br />\n<br />\n16/9諮詢期就過啦，之後拿拿聲上立法會一讀二讀三讀搞掂。<br />\n<br />\n#要消滅一個文化 #先消滅佢嘅語言<br />\n<br />\n學校課程檢討專責小組&mdash;諮詢文件 <br />\n截止評論日期：二零一九年九月十六日<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/TF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Fattachment%2Ftc%2Fabout-edb%2Fpress%2Fconsultation%2FTF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAPilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=991f9f2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/TF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n傳送門：<br />\n1. 摘要 p.ii<br />\n2. 小組建議 p.16<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：【中文課程改革1】DSE中文刪聆聽、說話　前線老師批「行回頭路」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/354111\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F354111&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAPilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=efb0ab52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/354111</a><br />\n<br />\nEmail Template:<br />\n學校課程檢討專責小組祕書處執事先生道鑒：<br />\n<br />\n（正文）<br />\n1. 表達立場：反對中文科刪卷三卷四<br />\n2. 提出原因：<br />\n3. 叫佢有乜野覆返你： 聯絡方法<br />\n<br />\n（格兩格）祝<br />\n道安<br />\n<br />\n香港市民（置右）<br />\nXxx謹啟（置右）<br />\n2019年8月15日（置左）"},{"pid":"1c4591bd9129feb7d7d23d052730e66ba62a06ce","tid":1488191,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T05:56:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">何文匯條臭𨳊,一早收閪左中共錢,十幾廿年黎一直用正音去&quot;變&quot;廣東話做普通話.死閪中共一早想亡廣東話</span>"},{"pid":"15d8a6ca39051fb5e9cf5c763fd0de23a8a108d1","tid":1488191,"uid":107639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T01:59:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23c948dcb33264e178c7225d1a945ba97a0778a7","tid":1488191,"uid":104432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:00:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1759a77bd21cd2a45d91a273c7d1f7ce1dfbf755","tid":1488191,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:01:03.000Z","msg":"出POST打錯日期 應該係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8月28同8月29號</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港自由之書&mdash;&mdash;報應來了，街站收集投訴信</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1510955/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1510955/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"f46e42d6acb165c32c7a904059235ee8f67863f3","tid":1488191,"uid":186576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T02:05:04.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e211c2d6921a718360f378f9fbd422247639a5f8","tid":1488191,"u